videos.description: When pressed about a possible future at Arkansas, Gus Malzahn insists he's happy at Auburn and wants to return as coach next year.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Presser (Malzahn: 'I'm happy here at Auburn') 2017/12/02

videos.headline: Malzahn: 'I'm happy here at Auburn'

videos.description: Auburn head coach Gus Malzahn shares the various injuries Kerryon Johnson played through against a Georgia defense that held him to 44 yards on 13 carries.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Presser(Malzahn: Johnson 'gave us all he had') 2017/12/02

videos.headline: Malzahn: Johnson 'gave us all he had'

videos.description: Auburn head coach Gus Malzahn believes the future is bright for the SEC conference and his team.

videos.headline: Malzahn says SEC 'is the best conference in football'

videos.description: Georgia head coach Kirby Smart says winning the SEC at his alma mater is "special", but even more special was seeing his players celebrate their victory together.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Presser (For Smart, it's about the players) 2017/12/02

videos.headline: For Smart, it's about the players

videos.description: Reflecting on their SEC Championship victory, Kirby Smart thanks the Georgia seniors and says they've "earned the honor of being SEC champs."
videos.headline: Smart thanks his seniors

videos.description: Georgia head coach Kirby Smart says Bo Jackson asked him about the pressure he faces before the SEC Championship.
